![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b49ac757-ae13-470d-a8c0-aa265603e8d9/Screenshot+2026-01-27+233013.png?format=original)

This week on the Major Issues Podcast, the hosts turn their attention to Absolute Superman, unpacking DC’s latest reimagining of the Man of Steel. From its creative vision and tonal shift to how it reshapes Clark Kent, Krypton, and Superman’s place in the world, the episode breaks down what makes this version distinct from traditional interpretations. The discussion explores the themes at the heart of Absolute Superman, how it fits into the broader Absolute Universe, and whether this bold reinvention captures the essence of what Superman represents. It is a focused, thoughtful dissection of one of DC’s most ambitious Superman stories in years.

